0:{"buildId":"7h74Y9z83_3h3-U7doOR4","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"x:mx-auto x:flex x:max-w-(--nextra-content-width)","children":["$","$L2",null,{"value":[{"value":"Color intents","id":"color-intents","depth":2},{"value":"Surface colors","id":"surface-colors","depth":2}],"children":[["$","$L3",null,{}],["$","$L4",null,{"metadata":{"title":"Colors","filePath":"content/foundation/colors.mdx"},"sourceCode":"# Colors\n\n색상은 **의도(intent)** 단위로 정의되며, 각 의도마다 surface / text / border / weak 등 변형이 있습니다.\n\n## Color intents\n\n| Intent     | 용도 예시                    |\n| ---------- | ---------------------------- |\n| primary    | 메인 CTA, 강조               |\n| secondary  | 보조 액션, 덜 강조된 요소     |\n| success    | 성공, 완료, 확인             |\n| warning    | 경고, 주의                   |\n| danger     | 삭제, 오류, 위험             |\n| neutral    | 배경, 테두리, 비강조 텍스트   |\n\n각 intent에는 다음 토큰이 있습니다.\n\n- **surface** — 배경\n- **surfaceHover** — 호버 시 배경\n- **surfaceActive** — 활성/누름 시 배경\n- **text** — 텍스트\n- **border** — 테두리\n- **weak** — 약한 강도(배경/텍스트)\n\n## Surface colors\n\n화면 전체 배경·텍스트용 토큰입니다.\n\n- **background** — 기본 배경\n- **backgroundElevated** — 카드·모달 등 상위 레이어 배경\n- **outline** — 아웃라인/포커스 링\n- **text** — 기본 텍스트\n- **textMuted** — 보조 텍스트\n- **divider** — 구분선\n\n컴포넌트의 `intent` prop(예: Button의 `intent=\"primary\"`)은 이 토큰과 연결됩니다.","children":[["$","div",null,{"id":"nextra-skip-nav"}],["$","main",null,{"data-pagefind-body":true,"children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-bold x:mt-2 x:text-4xl","children":["Colors","$undefined"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:leading-7","children":["색상은 ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"의도(intent)"}]," 단위로 정의되며, 각 의도마다 surface / text / border / weak 등 변형이 있습니다."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"color-intents","className":"x:tracking-tight x:text-slate-900 x:dark:text-slate-100 x:font-semibold x:target:animate-[fade-in_1.5s] x:mt-10 x:border-b x:pb-1 x:text-3xl nextra-border","children":["Color intents",["$","$L5",null,{"id":"color-intents"}]]}],"\n",["$","table",null,{"className":"x:block x:overflow-x-auto nextra-scrollbar x:not-first:mt-[1.25em] x:p-0","children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"Intent","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"용도 예시","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:font-semibold x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"primary","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"메인 CTA, 강조","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"secondary","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"보조 액션, 덜 강조된 요소","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"success","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"성공, 완료, 확인","className":"x:m-0 x:border x:border-gray-300 x:px-4 x:py-2 x:dark:border-gray-600"}]],"className":"x:m-0 x:border-t x:border-gray-300 x:p-0 x:dark:border-gray-600 x:even:bg-gray-100 x:even:dark:bg-gray-600/20"}],"$L6","$L7","$L8"]}]]}],"\n","$L9","\n","$La","\n","$Lb","\n","$Lc"